{
  "stem": "21786.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- the man responsible, the block Eltester, the head of the block, had to prepare everybody into attention and report, there are so and so many, and so and so many prisoners.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this-- this was not done, for nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody left with the transport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was talking about luck or no luck, I was the first one who was there, doing the knots on the-- on this so-called stretcher.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I stood into attention and clicked heels.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I reported that prisoner number 10065765 reports, block number 32 with so and so many prisoners, so and so many prisoners sick, so and so many prisoners died, so and so many prisoners working at preparing the stretchers.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I says, preparing the stretchers according to the ordinance number so and so which we got in the morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the SS man looked at me and said to one of these lower rank SS men, take his number.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he took my number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we were standing, then, in the morning at the appell-- so we somehow managed to arrange ourselves to five.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly a number was called from the SS barracks, which were, I mean, down outside of the camp, one kilometer from the-- far from the place I was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for the third time, they called the number.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I realized it's my number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I head-- I ran down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, you couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For [GERMAN], 'A prisoner moves while jogging.' For years, I couldn't understand why I cannot jog.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it dawned upon me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I jogged down, and then the SS man simply said to another guy, the other SS man there, gives it to him.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
